The Sun Products Corporation, a Henkel Company
Effective September 1, 2016, Henkel acquired the US laundry and home care company The Sun Products Corporation. With a transaction volume of around 3.2 billion euros, the acquisition is the second largest in Henkel’s history. The acquisition is a step-change for the business, with Henkel reaching the No. 2 position in the North American laundry care market. Sun Products’ portfolio includes well-known and successful brands such as all and Sun detergent and Snuggle fabric conditioner. And, the Company serves as a manufacturer and marketing partner to many of North America’s leading retailers, with a store brand portfolio of laundry and dish care products.




